1
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,039
Yan Mingli.

2
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,020
You have suffered.

3
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,060
I will save you.

4
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:27,760
But,

5
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,980
is it my father's idea?

6
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,240
It's my own idea.

7
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,640
This is a capital crime that involves your entire family.

8
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,520
All I know is

9
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:40,000
I can't let you wait for death in prison.

10
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:43,320
Go.

11
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,800
Notify the Chief Minister of Dali Temple.

12
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,200
Xie Yuheng has broken out of prison.

13
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,600
Issue an arrest warrant.

14
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,200
Send a copy to Mr. Xie.

15
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,930
Let Xie Wanshu take a good look.

16
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,800
He poured his heart and soul

17
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:14,840
into raising a son who brings honor to his ancestors.

18
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,520
Yes, My Lord.

19
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,280
Pandu.

20
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,040
Master!

21
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,960
Somebody come quick!

22
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,000
Help!

23
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,760
Master is having a stroke!

24
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,000
You went to see my father.

25
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,220
Is he still in good health?

26
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,920
Master Xie.

27
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,200
The servants in the manor take good care of me.

28
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:14,960
I am fine.

29
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,920
Thank you, sir.

30
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,770
It was no trouble at all. Don't mention it.

31
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:05,850
Farewell, miss.

32
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,160
Brother Xie, your hero-saving-the-beauty move

33
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,220
was truly dashing.

34
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:18,680
Could it be that you are smitten

35
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:21,519
and have fallen for the second miss of the Yan family?

36
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,380
The second miss of the Yan family?

37
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,260
Yan Mingli.

38
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,080
Indeed.

39
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,360
You are the eldest legitimate son of the Minister of Works.

40
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,720
If we are talking about marriage,

41
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:33,080
only the eldest legitimate daughter of the Duke's mansion would be a good match.

42
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:33,680
Stop looking.

43
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,540
Let's go to the tavern for a drink.

44
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:42,800
Qingshu.

45
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,650
I will ask you one more time.

46
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,680
Do you really want to marry Xie Yuheng?

47
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,409
Xie Yuheng treats me very well.

48
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,520
He puts me first in everything.

49
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,760
Why can't I marry him?

50
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:01,880
Sister.

51
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,530
Are you really going to marry into the Xie family?

52
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,080
Sister.

53
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:10,920
Yuheng and I love each other.

54
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,400
And he said

55
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:15,060
that I am the only one for him in this life.

56
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,220
Why shouldn't I marry him?

57
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,080
Yuheng.

58
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:33,000
After what happened between us that night.

59
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,120
Have you ever thought

60
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,570
about taking responsibility?

61
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,320
I am now

62
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,120
a wanted criminal by the court.

63
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,440
Hiding everywhere like a stray dog.

64
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,930
My life is on the edge of a blade.

65
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,200
I can barely protect myself.

66
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,560
How could a stray dog like me

67
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,480
dare to cling to the Duke's estate?

68
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:23,080
Wouldn't that ruin the good name of the Second Miss Yan?

69
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,480
Are you afraid you are not good enough,

70
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,240
or do you always feel deep down

71
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,640
that a concubine-born second daughter like me

72
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:33,900
is unworthy of the legitimate eldest son of the Xie family?

73
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,360
Given the current situation in the court.

74
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,360
Anyone with eyes can see it clearly.

75
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,960
The late Emperor's former right-hand men.

76
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,280
One died in battle,

77
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,040
and the other's whereabouts are a mystery.

78
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,840
The situation

79
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,200
is no longer what it used to be.

80
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,040
The Duke has been missing for over three years.

81
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,170
Alive or dead, there is no trace of him.

82
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,660
It's like a stone dropped into the ocean.

83
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,410
Do you know, Brother Wu,

84
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:15,410
who the Duke saw the night before he disappeared?

85
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,800
His Highness, Prince Ling.

86
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,880
According to what you said, Brother Li,

87
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:27,320
the Duke accepted Prince Ling's invitation

88
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,600
and met with misfortune.

89
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,520
Mind your words, Brother Wu.

90
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,960
I never said such a thing.

91
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,600
That is all your own speculation.

92
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,130
It has nothing to do with me.

93
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,159
Yes, it's my loose tongue.

94
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,920
I was overthinking and speaking nonsense.

95
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,720
Come, Brother Li, let's drink.

96
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:47,860
If my father's disappearance is truly related to Prince Ling,

97
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:49,280
what can I do now?

98
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,360
And what should I do?

99
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:57,400
Bitter almond, pinellia, cocklebur,

100
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,640
aconite, and nux vomica.

101
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,130
One ingredient is missing.

102
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:20,120
Bone-corroding, gut-piercing Tiannanxing.

103
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,480
This is a premium boudoir.

104
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,380
But you've smoked it into a big pharmacy.

105
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:44,280
Are you going to practice medicine and save the world,

106
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,080
or bring disaster to the people?

107
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,800
How much Tiannanxing should be used?

108
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:52,290
What medicine is needed to counteract its toxicity?

109
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,320
There's a palace banquet tomorrow night.

110
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,580
It must be very lively.

111
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,330
Do you want to go and see?

112
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,840
Perhaps I should go to Yaowang Valley,

113
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,240
and ask Aunt Qin.

114
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,360
Qingshu.

115
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,760
Yan Qingshu.

116
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,980
Do you want to see for yourself

117
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:20,200
the chess player behind the Prince of Ling?

118
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,520
Brother Jingyan, look.

119
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,000
My newly dyed nails.

120
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,330
Does this color suit me?

121
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:06,840
Take another look.

122
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,900
Hurry up and tell me if they look good.

123
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,850
Are you okay?

124
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,000
I'm fine.

125
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:36,960
Who is kneeling below the steps?

126
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:38,440
I, Qingshu,

127
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,920
danced improperly and lost my manners.

128
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,720
I startled Your Majesty.

129
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:44,970
I deserve to die.

130
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:47,920
I beg Your Majesty to punish me.

131
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,160
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

132
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,280
The music just now

133
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:59,720
was truly magnificent and powerful.

134
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,160
I think

135
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,660
Miss Yan must have been deeply moved.

136
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,640
She was so immersed in it

137
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:07,100
that she slipped and fell.

138
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:09,210
It was completely unintentional.

139
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,520
I hope the Empress Dowager will consider this her first offense,

140
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,560
and excusable,

141
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,770
and spare her from punishment.

142
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,000
Just a small mistake in the dance steps.

143
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,000
Why should it result in punishment?

144
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,810
Today's palace banquet

145
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:27,200
was meant to make me smile

146
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,760
and relieve the loneliness of the deep palace.

147
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,960
I actually feel that

148
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,720
the more unexpected it is,

149
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:37,320
the more interesting it is,

150
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,440
and it makes me happy.

151
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,480
Yan Qingshu,

152
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,960
you may rise.

153
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:47,760
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

154
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:57,100
Brother Jingyan is really tender toward women.

155
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,080
Why?

156
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:01,100
Are you familiar with that Duke's daughter?

157
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,200
I will take my leave.

158
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,330
I will take my leave.

159
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:25,840
Help!

160
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,800
Cuimei.

161
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:57,680
Yong.

162
00:13:58,400 --> 00:13:58,930
Huachao.

163
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,240
Weikun, Huachao.

164
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:03,520
Longcong, Biaohao.

165
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,170
Shuang, Bin.

166
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,080
Ning Zheng.

167
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,740
Ning Zheng.

168
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:12,640
Haochun, Kangshuaihua.

169
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,370
Weichao.

170
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,800
Qiangyuan, Liangbo.

171
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:34,880
Xi.

172
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:35,280
Xi.

173
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:36,800
Xi.

174
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:37,680
Taoqiang, Xi.

175
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,400
Taoqiang.

176
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,680
Huiyue, Yunqing.

177
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,880
Yiyi.

178
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:55,920
Si, Si.
